name: The Spencer Sisters
overview: Former police officer Darby Spencer and her mystery novelist mother Victoria Spencer have opposite personalities but still embark on the unlikeliest of ventures: becoming partners in a private detective agency. They are mistaken as sisters as they tackle puzzling cases in Alder Bluffs.

episodes.name: The Scholar's Snafu
episodes.overview: After her life in the city falls apart, former cop Darby is forced to return to her childhood home and her estranged, novelist mother. When Darby's friend Kaia is wrongfully accused of plagiarism, Darby and Victoria must put aside their differences and investigate, uncovering a wide-ranging scandal.

episodes.name: The Executive's Elegy
episodes.overview: When pharmaceutical CEO Marlina comes home to find her fiancé drowned, Victoria and Darby investigate whether he was a victim of corporate espionage or Marlina’s own progeny.

episodes.name: The Coder's Calamity
episodes.overview: Darby and Victoria investigate stolen intellectual property for a trio of Silicon Valley-style tech developers.

episodes.name: The Restauranteur's Ruin
episodes.overview: When local bistro owner Antonio's professional reputation is targeted, he seeks out Darby and Victoria's investigative services.

episodes.name: The Decorator's Debacle
episodes.overview: Darby and Victoria team up with Victoria's excitable friend Rory to investigate what he is sure was an attempt on his life.

episodes.name: The Winemaker's Woe
episodes.overview: Darby and Victoria are hired by a former schoolmate of Darby's to investigate acts of vandalism at his winery.

episodes.name: The Lawyer's Lament
episodes.overview: Darby's ex Lucas hires the Spencer sisters to look into a series of escalating threats against his fiancée Lindsay.

episodes.name: The Virtuoso's Vexation
episodes.overview: Darby and Victoria are hired by the director of an elite music academy to recover a priceless stolen violin.

episodes.name: The Diva's Disaster
episodes.overview: The actress who played 'Bryn Martell' in the movies based on Victoria's books, calls Victoria after she's accused of the attempted murder of her co-star.

episodes.name: The Runaway's Regret
episodes.overview: When Billy is kidnapped, Victoria and Darby have to set aside their differences to save him and figure out the truth behind his identity.
